<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
<title>Platform · __PRIMARY_DOMAIN__</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117; --surface: #161b22; --surface-hover: #1f2630;
    --border: #30363d; --text: #e6edf3; --muted: #8b949e; --accent: #58a6ff;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg); color: var(--text);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5; min-height: 100vh; padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 920px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { padding: 1rem 0 1.5rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; }
  header .domain { color: var(--muted); font-size: .95rem; margin-top: .15rem; }
  h2 {
    font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .06em; color: var(--muted); margin: 2rem 0 .85rem;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid; gap: .85rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
  }
  .card {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .25rem;
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    text-decoration: none; color: var(--text);
    transition: background .12s ease, border-color .12s ease;
  }
  .card:hover { background: var(--surface-hover); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .card:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset: 2px; }
  .card-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.02rem; }
  .card-desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; }
  .card-host {
    color: var(--accent); font-size: .8rem; margin-top: .35rem;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .panel {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
  }
  .panel p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .92rem; }
  .panel code {
    display: block; margin-top: .7rem; padding: .7rem .85rem;
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: .85rem; color: var(--text); overflow-x: auto;
  }
  footer {
    margin-top: 2.5rem; padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted); font-size: .82rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) { body { padding: 1rem; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <header>
    <h1>Platform</h1>
    <div class="domain">__PRIMARY_DOMAIN__</div>
  </header>

  <h2>Tools</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    __CLAUDE_CARD__
    __DOZZLE_CARD__
    __GLANCES_CARD__
    __NTOPNG_CARD__
    __GRAFANA_CARD__
    <a class="card" href="https://auth.__PRIMARY_DOMAIN__">
      <span class="card-name">Authelia</span>
      <span class="card-desc">SSO portal and your 2FA settings</span>
      <span class="card-host">auth.__PRIMARY_DOMAIN__</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2>Users</h2>
  <div class="panel">
    <p>
      Every tool above is gated by Authelia single sign-on (password + TOTP).
      To grant someone access, add an Authelia user from an SSH session on the
      server:
    </p>
    <code>sudo /opt/infra/platform/authelia/add-user.sh &lt;username&gt;</code>
    <p style="margin-top:.7rem">
      The script sets the password, enrols a TOTP device, and prints the
      enrolment QR for the new user to scan.
    </p>
  </div>

  <footer>
    Platform layer · gated by Authelia SSO · served by Caddy.
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
